{"data":[{"id":564183228,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7c892171ce83354e0919a26a838b1722","url_token":"dragon-60-58-93","name":"dragon","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-597cb5f14ef75608d684a76f40f2ef78_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-597cb5f14ef75608d684a76f40f2ef78_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7c892171ce83354e0919a26a838b1722","user_type":"people","headline":"蘑菇，溜哪路？","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":9,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564183228","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-dae5bbce28ce09fe5e27b509955dbdf1_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546339278,"updated_time":1546409724,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":12,"comment_count":3,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e先来看下几个高赞回答有问题的地方\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e\u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/b2f508e8f839b8870763f8085b1085fb\" data-hash=\"b2f508e8f839b8870763f8085b1085fb\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$b2f508e8f839b8870763f8085b1085fb\"\u003e@Monsieur TRISTE\u003c/a\u003e \u003cbr\u003e（这个逆否命题是没法证出来的，因为它的结论“-1不是负质数”与之前的假设“-1是负质数”矛盾。）\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e那个逆否命题没办法证出真假在于它的前提真假难以判定。不是因为结论……矛盾。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e\u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/9330ac152cd71a3d87bd2c46ed655749\" data-hash=\"9330ac152cd71a3d87bd2c46ed655749\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$9330ac152cd71a3d87bd2c46ed655749\"\u003e@陈沉沉\u003c/a\u003e 1.为什么逆反命题正确？\u003cbr\u003e结论为真，不管假设如何，命题恒为真。\u003cbr\u003e2.逻辑漏洞在哪里？\u003cbr\u003e假设为假，命题恒为真，结论不一定为真。例如：美女对舔狗说：男人都死绝了，我会嫁给你。该命题为真，但不能说美女嫁给舔狗是对的。\u003cbr\u003e3.回到原证明。如果把-1定义成质数，那么逆反命题不为真，证明错。如果把-1不定义成质数，那么假设为假，不能说明结论为真。\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e在-1归到质数集的前提下那个逆否命题的结论是错误的，而且它的前提是难以判断真假的。那么整个命题真假也就无从得知。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实这个出问题的地方关键在于\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e\u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7c90693ab3c4ce27c26ca300e932c302\" data-hash=\"7c90693ab3c4ce27c26ca300e932c302\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7c90693ab3c4ce27c26ca300e932c302\"\u003e@ghj123h\u003c/a\u003e 所说的在这个命题中 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1%5Cnotin%5Cmathbb%7BP%7D%5E%7B-%7D\" alt=\"-1\\notin\\mathbb{P}^{-}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 必然为假。若要证明此命题为真，需要证明“若 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cexists%7Bn_0%7D%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D_%2B%2C2n_0%5Cnotin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"\\exists{n_0}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n_0\\notin{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e”的部分（记为 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=p\" alt=\"p\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ）亦为假才能证明其为真。而这位高中生误以为说明 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2%5Cin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"2\\in{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 即可证明 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=p\" alt=\"p\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 为假。而实际上 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=p%3Dp_2%5Cvee%7Bp_4%7D%5Cvee%7Bp_6%7D%5Cvee%5Ccdots%2Cp_i%3Ai%5Cnotin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"p=p_2\\vee{p_4}\\vee{p_6}\\vee\\cdots,p_i:i\\notin{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，因此说明 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2%5Cin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"2\\in{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 并不能证明 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=p\" alt=\"p\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 为假。\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e下面，我将证明中的出现命题符号化而使其不会出现二义性，这些符号学过离散数学懂得数理逻辑基础的都应该非常清楚。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e设命题P:(∃n)(n∈N+∧2*n∉A),Q:-1不是质数。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b6ad28a809491a7bffa06b6660437fac_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"591\" data-rawheight=\"440\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6bf6f1ff050d05d1f1a8bc9895ec36b7_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"591\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b6ad28a809491a7bffa06b6660437fac_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='591'%20height='440'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"591\" data-rawheight=\"440\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6bf6f1ff050d05d1f1a8bc9895ec36b7_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"591\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b6ad28a809491a7bffa06b6660437fac_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b6ad28a809491a7bffa06b6660437fac_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e红线所划部分是一个若P则Q型的命题，即可符号化为P→Q(等价于¬P∨Q)，其真值表是这样的:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-90dc9818ca3eb7c1c3151f2159c631c3_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"506\" data-rawheight=\"283\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-dc35c207230de4dfffff31ecb85cb4e6_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"506\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-90dc9818ca3eb7c1c3151f2159c631c3_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='506'%20height='283'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"506\" data-rawheight=\"283\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-dc35c207230de4dfffff31ecb85cb4e6_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"506\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-90dc9818ca3eb7c1c3151f2159c631c3_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-90dc9818ca3eb7c1c3151f2159c631c3_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e在他的假设-1属于质数集的前提下，结论Q的真值为假，只有前提P为假的情况下整个命题才为真，然后他了写这样一段话：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-da6236151a7555a4ba8948b6101f1807_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"655\" data-rawheight=\"89\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"655\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-da6236151a7555a4ba8948b6101f1807_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='655'%20height='89'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"655\" data-rawheight=\"89\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"655\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-da6236151a7555a4ba8948b6101f1807_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-da6236151a7555a4ba8948b6101f1807_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e实际上这并没有证明P为假，而且2∈A(因为把-1归到质数集集时2=-1＋3可以写成两个质数之和)，对P:(∃n)(n∈N+∧2*n∉A)这种含有存在量词的命题想要证明其真值为假的话，要从反面考虑即尝试对其否定¬P:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e¬(∃n)(n∈N+∧2*n∉A)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e⇔(∀n)¬(n∈N+∧2*n∉A)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e⇔(∀n)(n∉N+∨2*n∈A)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e⇔(∀n)(n∈N+→2*n∈A)证其真值为真。其实到这里属于绕了一圈又回到原命题\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7b6d67369165972ae2d446ce3e80cb35_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"454\" data-rawheight=\"59\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"454\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7b6d67369165972ae2d446ce3e80cb35_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='454'%20height='59'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"454\" data-rawheight=\"59\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"454\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7b6d67369165972ae2d446ce3e80cb35_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7b6d67369165972ae2d446ce3e80cb35_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e的结论了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e再者，我们难以判定这个¬P的真假情况。为什么？我们会陷入两难的境地，难以从正面说它是真命题，证其真值为真理论上要比证哥德巴赫猜想本身为真命题难度要小，从反面试图证伪的话又像我们很难证明哥德巴赫猜想为假一样(尽管我们只需要找到一个大于2的偶数不能写为两质数之和的反例即可)我们也很难证明¬P:(∀n)(n∈N+→2*n∈A)为假(即证明某个正偶数不在A之中)，而且这个证伪难度要大于对证明哥德巴赫猜想证伪本身。接下来我说明其证伪难度大于对哥德巴赫猜想证伪本身的理由。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先来看下集合A的定义：设集合A为所有满足两个质数之和的偶数的集合。且此时质数包括正质数和负质数。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当他把-1放进质数集里面的时候就更加增加了一个正偶数可以写成两个质数之和的可能性，在原本质数集没有-1的情况下我们都难找到一个反面特例即某个大于2的偶数不能写成两个质数之和，况且还增加了一个数-1，增加了–1之后甚至于把原本2这个不能写成两个质数(这个质数所属的质数集是不包含–1的原原本本的质数集)之和的偶数都可以写成-1和3这个两个“质数”(加引号的表示属于扩充后的质数集)之和了。如果说质数集可以随便扩充的话，那么我和这位高中生类似，先把质数集扩充为复数集(即复数集就是质数集)，然后说任何一个正偶数都可以写成两个质数(复数)之和，ok，这时候对¬P:(∀n)(n∈N+→2*n∈A)证伪将变得不可能，因为这时候任意偶数肯定可以写为两个“质数”(复数)之和，也即¬P将成为一个永真式。但是可别忘了我是试图证明¬P为假的，因为扩充了质数集证其为假的可能性将越来越渺茫，而且只要一扩充这个证明难度就要比对哥德巴赫猜想证伪还要大。换句话说，如果能在扩充后的质数集上对¬P:(∀n)(n∈N+→2*n∈A)证得其真值为假，那么哥德巴赫猜想也一定是一个假命题(因为对¬P证其为假命题需要找到一个偶数不能写为两个扩充后的“质数”集里面的“质数”之和，那么它更不能写为原本质数集里两个质数之和，毕竟后者只是前者的一个子集罢了)。尽管其证伪难度比对哥德巴赫猜想证伪还要大，也不能说明¬P就是一个真命题。总之，这位高中生所做的工作基本上到这里就难以进行下去了。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"先来看下几个高赞回答有问题的地方\u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/b2f508e8f839b8870763f8085b1085fb\" data-hash=\"b2f508e8f839b8870763f8085b1085fb\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$b2f508e8f839b8870763f8085b1085fb\"\u003e@Monsieur TRISTE\u003c/a\u003e （这个逆否命题是没法证出来的，因为它的结论“-1不是负质数”与之前的假设“-1是负质数”矛盾。）那个逆否命题没办法证出真假在于它的前提真假难以判定。不是因为结论……矛盾。\u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/9330ac152cd71a3d87bd2c46ed655749\" data-hash=\"9330ac152cd71a3d87bd2c46ed655749\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$9330ac152cd71a3d87bd2c46ed655749\"\u003e@陈沉沉\u003c/a\u003e 1.为什么逆反命…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=94\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=92\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","totals":489}}
